Indomie Instant noodles, has announced the kick-off of its nationwide consumer promotion tagged ‘Indomitables Magnet Promo’ with millions of naira. The company in a statement released to LEADERSHIP Sunday, said that the three month promo will run from February 25 to May 25, 2020. It stated that “Consumers are expected to participate and win any of the available prizes by buying a promo pack or carton of ‘Indomitables’ Indomie noodles, open a pack to get a free magnet and a chance to win other instant prizes. “Consumers stand a chance to win a redeemable gift by sending a picture of the image on the magnet with their name and address to the number provided on the pack via Whatsapp. They will then get a confirmation message on how to redeem their prize.” Speaking on the new promo, the Group Public Relations and Events Manager of the Company, Tope Ashiwaju said the promo is an avenue to express the company’s appreciation to its loyal customers for their continuous patronage and support. According to Ashiwaju, “Indomie is the number one noodles brand in Nigeria and so we consider it an obligation to connect with our numerous consumers, while building excitement in appreciation of their loyalty to the brand.” Ashiwaju said participants in the promo, will have the opportunity to win over N100 million worth of prizes across Nigeria within the three months duration of the promo. He noted that the plan is to ensure that everyone who participates wins something as the promotion is expected to produce at least 100,000 winners, listing the prizes to be won to include, iPads, bicycles, school bags, lunch bags, lots of Indomie noodles cartons as well as other consolation prizes. The Indomie ‘Indomitables’ comprises five super heroes, whose mission is to protect the world from man-made disasters perpetrated by villains.